&lt;li&gt;Follow daily checklist and activity schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain continuous participant observation for safety and therapeutic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with admissions, discharges, and participant orientation.&lt;/li&gt;
